
------------------
 X-INVASION V.1.0
------------------

1- INTRODUCTION:

 This game is a simple clone of famous game SPACE INVADERS
 with varius level, more graphic and end of level guardians.
 In game is included a version for nostalgic peole of the 
 original SPACE INVADERS fromATARI VCS 2600

2- HOW TO INSTALL:

 The game can be istalled in the hard disk, it needs the AMOS.LIBRARY 
 in directory LIBS, ( you can found the library in install.lha file ), 
 the program also needs the DISKFONT.LIBRARY ( in LIBS ). 
 To Install Program in an Hard Disk you must copy the follow
 files and directory in a new drawer:

  A> Intro
  B> XInvasion

  A> DATA
  B> MUSIC
  C> IFF

 To run the game just double click on icon XInvasion or Intro
 ( to see the introduction ).

3- KEYS:

 To play you need a JOYSTICK.
 There are some options inside the menu' OPTION like:

 A> START GAME (Start Game Immediatly)
 B> OPTION     (Go to OPTION menu)
  B1> (Game Mode CLASSIC/NEW STYLE)
  B2> (Numbers of ife)
  B3> (Start game)
  B4> (Exit)

4- YOU NEED:

 The game run correctly in any Amiga with 1 Mb of RAM.

